| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3059 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 17ab687e-1b9f-57b2-bdb3-a35c15f3c970"
